# batteryctl - Battery health and power management

> macOS command-line utility (Rust)

## Project Overview

**Type:** Command-line utility (Rust)
**Purpose:** Battery health and power management
**Platform:** macOS (Apple Silicon & Intel)

## Features

- Battery health monitoring
- Charge cycle tracking
- Charging status and rate
- Power consumption analysis
- Battery temperature monitoring
- Estimated runtime calculations

## Development

```bash
# Build
cargo build

# Run
cargo run -- [ARGS]

# Test
cargo test

# Format and lint
cargo fmt
cargo clippy

# Build release
cargo build --release
```

## Installation

```bash
# Install locally
cargo install --path .

# Build and copy to system
cargo build --release
cp target/release/batteryctl /usr/local/bin/
```

## Usage

```bash
# Show help
batteryctl --help

# Show version
batteryctl --version
```
